$interpreted: Mr. Waits: It's not ready yet?? You've been fixing her for hours! I spent a lot of money on you!
Rune Sorcerer: Artifacts from the Mechanical Territory are quite rare, however...the Rune activation process should be about the same.
Rune Sorcerer: Turn it on.
Mr. Waits: How do I do that?
Rune Sorcerer: Press here.
Mr. Waits: I-I-I didn't expect it to be here...
Maria: Backup Core restart complete. Please confirm user. Please state user's name or create new user.
Mr. Waits: *cough*...I'm Waits! From now on, I'm your master!
Rune Sorcerer: Although I can't delete the data stored in the Main Core, it should be able to accept a new user...
Maria: Creating new user "Waits".
Mr. Waits: Oh!? It worked!?
Maria: Master Waits, awaiting next command!
Mr. Waits: Hehehe...Hahaha...Wahahah!!!!
Clark: I've been searching for half a day and all I found was a malfunctioning Chu Chu. Maybe she thought of something and left...
Clark: *sigh*...what a hassle...
Wife: Excuse me...I heard that you fix Rune items?
Clark: Welcome, welcome. What may I help you with?
Wife: Can-Can it be fixed?
Clark: This...looks like it's pretty badly damaged. I'm afraid this will be quite difficult...
Wife: *sob*...*sob*...this was part of my inheritance from my mother! If it can't be fixed, I-I-I...
Husband: Honey, don't cry. I'll go find those hooligans and make 'em pay!
Wife: Please, no! If you're hurt by that monster, I don't know what I'll do!
Clark: Monster? What monster?
Husband: In the Old City, there's a bunch of thugs who have been taking a girl around with them to rob and steal.
Husband: Since they couldn't get anything from us, they just broke our vendor booth. Everything's a mess!
Wife: Th-Th-That girl can even fly. She's got to be a monster! Even our son was beaten by her...*sob*...*sob*...
Clark: I...I know...I can fix this clock, don't you worry about it.
Clark: Come back in a few days.
Wife: Thank you so much, sir.
Maria: *ping* *clank* *BOOM*...Hahaha! What fun~
Mr. Waits: Pay attention Gramps! If you don't pay your protection fee, this is what happens!
Grandpa: Si-Sir! I don't have any money, I mean it!
Mr. Waits: Since you don't have any money, then how do you do business?
Young Fella': Grandpa! Grandpa, are you okay!? You scum! Take this!
Maria: Do not hurt Master Waits!
Mr. Waits: Wah! You want to hurt me? You've got guts, kid. Maria, kill him!
Maria: Command received, Master Waits!
Clark: Maria, stop!
Maria: Master Clark!
Clark: Maria, help the old man up!
Maria: Yes! Maria is obeying orders!
Mr. Waits: Hey! What the hell is this?
Rune Sorcerer: *cough*...since the main core was not restarted, both you and this nut are both her masters.
Mr. Waits: What!? Blasted! Maria, get over here!
Clark: What are you going to do to her?
Mr. Waits: I'm Maria's master now! Don't you interfere with this!
Maria: You dare...
Mr. Waits: Maria, obey me! Kill this piece of dirt!
Maria: You dare hurt Master Clark...
Mr. Waits: Maria?
Grandpa: *shocked*...what a terrifying monster!
Clark: She's...she's not a monster, she's from the Mechanical Territory, that's all...
Clark: Maria, go tell everybody you're sorry immediately...
Maria: Yes! Maria is obeying orders!
Maria: I'm so sorry...I'm sorry...I am so sorry...
Young Fella': You...apologizing with a grin on your face!? You think I'm gonna accept that?
Grandpa: You bully! You...you...get the hell out of here! I don't want to see you again!
Maria: ???
Maria: Master Clark, why are they so angry?
Clark: Forgive me. I will repay you for all of this...we will leave immediately.
